# HomeschoolHQ: 8-Week Sprint to Launch
**Timeline**: Feb 10 - April 7, 2026
**Goal**: Launch Pro tier with working calendar integration differentiator

---

## Week 1: Feb 10-16 - Fix Calendar Sync Foundation
**Critical Path**: Get calendar sync working again

### Deliverables:
- [ ] Complete diagnostic tests (CALENDAR_SYNC_DEBUG_PLAN.md)
- [ ] Fix broken calendar sync
- [ ] All Phase 3 verification tests pass
- [ ] Calendar stays synced for 48+ hours without manual intervention
- [ ] Document what was fixed

### Success Metrics:
- ‚úÖ Events sync from Google Calendar to synced_work_events
- ‚úÖ Sync runs automatically every 15 minutes
- ‚úÖ No errors in logs for 48 hours

### Time Budget: 12-15 hours
- Diagnosis: 2 hours
- Fixes: 6-8 hours
- Testing: 2-3 hours
- Documentation: 2 hours

**DO NOT MOVE TO WEEK 2 UNTIL THIS WORKS PERFECTLY**

