## Week 3: Feb 24 - Mar 2 - Attendance & Vacation Integration
**Critical Path**: Make attendance respect vacations, show work context in vacation planning

### Deliverables:
- [ ] Attendance tracking excludes vacation days from "absent" count
- [ ] Attendance dashboard shows vacation days with different styling
- [ ] Vacation planning page shows work events as background context
- [ ] Test with your 3 test students

### Success Metrics:
- ‚úÖ Vacation day marked ‚Üí not counted as absent
- ‚úÖ Attendance card shows "3 vacation days this week" when relevant
- ‚úÖ Can see work meetings when planning vacation (avoid conflicts)

### Time Budget: 8-10 hours
- Attendance logic update: 3-4 hours
- Vacation page enhancement: 3-4 hours
- Testing: 2 hours

