## Week 4: Mar 3-9 - Conflict Detection & Warnings
**Critical Path**: Show conflict warnings when lesson overlaps work meeting

### Deliverables:
- [ ] Conflict detection service (check lesson time vs work events)
- [ ] Warning appears when creating/editing lesson that conflicts
- [ ] Store resolution in calendar_conflict_resolutions table
- [ ] UI shows warning with specific meeting details
- [ ] Parent can dismiss or reschedule

### Success Metrics:
- ‚úÖ Create lesson at 2pm when work meeting at 2pm ‚Üí see warning
- ‚úÖ Warning shows: "‚ö†Ô∏è Conflicts with Team Meeting (2:00-3:00 PM)"
- ‚úÖ Can click to reschedule or mark as "will work around it"

### Time Budget: 12-15 hours
- Conflict detection logic: 5-6 hours
- UI integration: 4-5 hours
- Resolution workflow: 2-3 hours
- Testing: 2 hours

### Technical Notes:
- Run conflict check on lesson create/update
- Check for time overlap (start < work.end AND end > work.start)
- Handle all-day events
- Handle recurring work events

